---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Be More Free - Alternative to Traditional Therapy">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-24 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 via-white to-accent-50"></div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">
        About <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-500">Be More Free</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-2xl text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        We believe everyone deserves to find their own answers without someone else's 
        agenda getting in the way.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Be More Free exists to provide a genuine alternative to traditional therapy 
            and coaching. We've seen too many people spend years in therapy with minimal 
            results, exhausted from managing coping mechanisms that don't actually help.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            That's why we developed the Neutral Zone process—a radically different approach 
            that helps people see themselves clearly and make real changes, often in hours 
            instead of years.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-accent-100 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why "Be More Free"?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Because that's what actually happens when you have space to examine your own 
            material without interference. You become more free from old patterns, more 
            free from others' expectations, more free to make your own choices.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Values Section -->
      <div class="mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">What We Stand For</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold mx-auto mb-6">
              1
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Your Wisdom Matters</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              You already have the answers within you. You just need the right space 
              to find them—without someone else's interpretations getting in the way.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500 to-accent-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold mx-auto mb-6">
              2
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">No One Above You</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We reject the traditional model where the practitioner is the expert 
              and you're the patient. In our process, no one has altitude over you.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-accent-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold mx-auto mb-6">
              3
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Real Results, Fast</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We're not interested in keeping you in sessions for years. 
              Our goal is to help you find what you're looking for as quickly as possible.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Who We Serve -->
      <div class="mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Who We Serve</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 to-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-l-4 border-primary-500">
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Be More Free serves people who are frustrated with traditional approaches to 
            personal growth. Our clients include:
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="text-primary-500 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>The Frustrated Seeker:</strong> You've tried therapy, coaching, 
                self-help books, and meditation apps, but still feel stuck
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="text-primary-500 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>The High Performer:</strong> You're successful but sabotaging 
                yourself and want efficient, real change
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="text-primary-500 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>The Therapy Skeptic:</strong> You want help but distrust 
                traditional therapeutic approaches
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="text-primary-500 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>The Truth Seeker:</strong> You're ready to look at what's 
                actually there, without someone else's agenda
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- The Difference -->
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">The Be More Free Difference</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
          We're not another therapy practice or coaching business. We're pioneers of a 
          completely different approach—one that actually helps you be more free.
        </p>
        
        <a href="/neutral-zone" 
           class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-semibold hover:shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 inline-flex items-center">
          Learn About Our Process
          <span class="ml-2">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-accent-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6">
        Ready to Be More Free?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Experience the difference for yourself with a free 30-minute trial session.
      </p>
      <a href="/booking/free-trial" 
         class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-500 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-full text-xl font-bold hover:shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 inline-flex items-center">
        Book Your Free Trial
        <span class="ml-3">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
